<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your SDS Login Details</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #1e3a5f; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .header p { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8; }
    .content { padding: 24px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .credentials-box { background: #ffffff; border: 2px solid #1e3a5f; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .credentials-box h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .credential-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
    .credential-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .credential-label { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
    .credential-value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }
    .login-number { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #1e3a5f; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 12px; background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 6px; margin: 8px 0 16px; }
    .steps { background: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #1e3a5f; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; margin: 16px 0; }
    .steps ol { margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 18px; }
    .steps li { font-size: 13px; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .website-link { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 24px; background-color: #1e3a5f; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 12px 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .warning { font-size: 12px; color: #b45309; background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 12px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Eswatini Career Guidance System</h1>
    <p>Ministry of Labour and Social Security · Kingdom of Eswatini</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

    <p>Your school has registered you on the <strong>Eswatini Career Guidance System</strong>. Below are your login details. Keep them safe — you will use the same Login Number throughout your school, university, and career journey.</p>

    <div class="credentials-box">
      <h3>Your Login Details</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 8px;">Your unique Login Number (use this to sign in for life):</p>
      <div class="login-number">{{studentCode}}</div>
      <div class="credential-row">
        <span class="credential-label">Password</span>
        <span class="credential-value">{{password}}</span>
      </div>
      {{#if grade}}
      <div class="credential-row">
        <span class="credential-label">Grade / Class</span>
        <span class="credential-value">{{grade}}{{#if className}} · {{className}}{{/if}}</span>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      <div class="credential-row">
        <span class="credential-label">Website</span>
        <span class="credential-value">{{loginUrl}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <strong style="font-size:13px;">How to get started:</strong>
      <ol>
        <li>Go to <strong>{{loginUrl}}</strong></li>
        <li>Enter your Login Number: <strong>{{studentCode}}</strong></li>
        <li>Enter your password above</li>
        <li>Complete the Career Guidance Assessment</li>
        <li>View and download your Career Report</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="website-link">Go to Career Guidance System</a>

    <div class="warning">
      ⚠️ <strong>Important:</strong> Please change your password after your first login. Keep your Login Number safe — it is your permanent account identifier.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 Ministry of Labour and Social Security — Kingdom of Eswatini</p>
    <p>This is an automated message. Do not reply to this email.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
